      "description": "\ud83d\ude97 $19,500 - A reliable ride at a wallet-friendly price! This vehicle is in fair condition \u2014 it runs dependably and handles daily commutes with ease, making it a smart pick for budget-savvy buyers. The interior and exterior show some normal wear consistent with its age, but nothing that gets in the way of a solid, functional driving experience. If you're looking for dependable transportation without breaking the bank, this one's worth a look!",
